The '''Chittagong City Center''' (also called '''City Center'''), is a {{convert|204.2|m|ft|abbr=off|sp=us}} proposed and approved 51-story tower in [[Agrabad|Agrabad Commercial Area]], [[Chittagong]]. If built to specifications, it would be the tallest building in the city and the tallest in [[Bangladesh]]. Style Living Architects Ltd is the designer and the developer of the [[skyscraper]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://skyscrapercenter.com/building/chittagong-city-center/17133 |title=Chittagong City Center |website=The Skyscraper Center |publisher=Council on Tall Buildings and Urban Habitat |access-date=19 October 2015}}</ref>
